                "text": "Let's solve the equation:\n\n\\[\n\\sin(x) + x^2 = 42\n\\]\n\nThis equation is nonlinear and cannot be solved analytically for \\( x \\). We'll use numerical methods to find its solution(s).\n\nWe'll look for real solutions. Let's proceed by plotting the function and using a numerical solver to find the value(s) of \\( x \\).",
